Our Reporter  JUST after celebrating his brother’s wedding in Abu Dhabi last weekend, it seems that Davido is still enjoying the Emirates. He took to Instagram to share what he has been up to since the celebrated wedding of HKN Chairman, Adewale Adeleke, who is also Davido’s elder brother. While the wedding took place at the Emirates Palace Hotel, Abu Dhabi, UAE last weekend, Davido showed he has been catching his fun.  On Thursday, he posted a picture of himself and his wife wearing caftans. While Davido wore a white caftan, his wife wore a black caftan. The DMW boss simply posted: ” Desert Day with the Wife.”